COA/Content/LevelPrototyping/
COA/Content/__ExternalActors__/
COA/Content/__ExternalObjects__/
COA/Content/Characters/
COA/Content/ThirdPerson/Lvl_ThirdPerson.umap
COA/Content/ThirdPerson/MI_ThirdPersonColWay.uasset


